headline.print_headline: Siemens Says Respects France's Decision on Alstom
headline.main: Siemens Says Respects France's Decision on Alstom

lead_paragraph: Siemens on Friday conceded in its battle to take over part of France's Alstom, after France rejected its offer with Mitsubishi Heavy Industries in favor of a rival bid from General Electric.
